      "content": "i hear you on the limited stock thing, but the supplier just emailed saying the shipment is stuck in transit for at least another 3 weeks. if we keep them listed and someone orders them today, they aren't getting those boots for a month. won't that tank our ratings and cause a massive wave of cancellations? isn't it better to just be honest and pull them now?",
