      "content": "the problem is if we put a \"low stock\" banner or an \"estimated date,\" people see that and it might hit our conversion rate even harder. if we just keep them listed as 'in stock' like normal, we might actually cruise through these last 15 units today before people even realize there's a delay. wouldn't it be easier to just keep the status as is and deal with the shipment delay once it actually arrives? wouldn't that keep our sales velocity much smoother?",
